    "secid:weakness/mitre.org/cwe#CWE-1427"
  ],
  "notes": "Some weakness sources require a version (OWASP Top 10 changes between editions — A01 means different things in 2017 vs 2021). Sources with version_required return all matching versions with disambiguation guidance when version is omitted.",
